snippet.title: Megaman X and Zero: Training Missions - Announcement Trailer (Fan Game)
snippet.description:
in the year 21XX...

Set between the events of X3 and X4, witness the grueling training that X and Zero undergo to prepare for the next Maverick outbreak!
==================
Made by Adam Kareem

Grab the demo today here!
https://gamejolt.com/@AdamKareem/games

Trailer Song:
"Megaman X Guiitar Medley" by Family Jules
https://youtu.be/APNQghAQlzM

This project is in no way affiliated with Capcom
